OL,3,CShop prices fall for first time in
OL,4,Cnearly three years
OL,6,FPrices in shops are falling for the
OL,7,Ffirst time in nearly three years, new
OL,8,Ffigures show.
OL,10,FRetailers slashing prices of fashion
OL,11,Fand household goods to get rid of
OL,12,Fsummer stock helped overall shop
OL,13,Fprices fall into deflation in August
OL,14,Ffor the first time since October 2021,
OL,15,Faccording to an influential retail
OL,16,Fgroup.
OL,18,FThe discounting followed a difficult
OL,19,Fsummer period for retailers due to
OL,20,Fpoor weather and the continuing cost-
OL,21,Fof-living crisis.
