OL,3,CShop prices fall for first time in
OL,4,Cnearly three years
OL,6,FShop prices in August were 0.3% lower
OL,7,Fthan a year earlier, the British
OL,8,FRetail Consortium found.
OL,10,FThe figure is down from inflation of
OL,11,F0.2% in July and below the three-month
OL,12,Faverage rate of 0%. The survey period
OL,13,Fcovered the first week of August.
OL,15,FThe overall decline was driven by the
OL,16,Fdeflation of 1.5% of "non-food"
OL,17,Fproducts, which refers to products
OL,18,Flike clothing, furniture and
OL,19,Felectronics.
